I think there's an issue with hex values.  For example:

 > 0xa_2
[1] 162
 > 0x2_a
Error: unexpected input in "0x2_"

So "a" counts as a digit in 0xa_2, but not as a digit in 0x2_a.

Duncan Murdoch


